# This project now uses Supabase directly from the React app.
# You do not need server/.env for the Supabase static-site version.
# Put browser-safe values in the root .env.local file instead:
#
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-supabase-anon-key
# VITE_SUPABASE_PHOTO_BUCKET=eulogy-photos
